'''重型洲際彈道飛彈'''（{{lang-en|Heavy ICBM}}）是在1970年代創建的術語，用來描述一類[[蘇聯|蘇聯]]和[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]][[洲際彈道飛彈|洲際彈道飛彈]]。<ref name=graham2003>{{cite book |title=Cornerstones of Security: Arms Control Treaties in the Nuclear Era |last=Graham |first=Thomas, Jr. |author2=Damien J. La Vera |pages=336 et al. |year=2003 |publisher=[[University_of_Washington_Press|University of Washington Press]] |isbn=9780295982960 }}</ref>它們的特點是重達5至9公噸，是[[LGM-30義勇兵洲際彈道飛彈|LGM-30義勇兵洲際彈道飛彈]]的數倍，長度超過35米，因此能夠在一枚[[多目標重返大氣層載具|多目標重返大氣層載具]](MIRV)中發射大量彈頭。

該術語通常指的是R-36 /“ SS-9 Scarp”<ref name=SS-9>{{cite web|title=R-36 / SS-9 SCARP|url=http://www.fas.org/nuke/guide/russia/icbm/r-36.htm|publisher=www.fas.org|accessdate=19 October 2012|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126070113/https://fas.org/nuke/guide/russia/icbm/r-36.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，R-36M（SS-18）變體/“ SS-18 Satan”<ref name=graham2003/><ref name=ss18>{{cite web|title=R-36M / SS-18 SATAN|url=http://www.fas.org/nuke/guide/russia/icbm/r-36m.htm|publisher=www.fas.org|accessdate=19 October 2012|archive-date=2021-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210323214849/https://fas.org/nuke/guide/russia/icbm/r-36m.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，和RS-28 Sarmat /“  SS-X-32 SNOWFLAKE”導彈。

RS-28 Sarmat被稱為“超重型”洲際彈道飛彈。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.rt.com/news/363981-russian-icbm-sarmat-missile/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-01-09 |archive-date=2021-01-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121124552/https://www.rt.com/news/363981-russian-icbm-sarmat-missile/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=Gady|first=Franz-Stefan|title=Russia Upgrades Facility to Produce RS-28 Sarmat ICBM|url=https://thediplomat.com/2020/03/russia-upgrades-facility-to-produce-rs-28-sarmat-icbm/|access-date=2021-01-06|website=thediplomat.com|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210329061609/https://thediplomat.com/2020/03/russia-upgrades-facility-to-produce-rs-28-sarmat-icbm/|dead-url=no}}</ref>超重型洲際彈道飛彈的歷史可追溯到UR-500，後者旨在提供50兆噸（可能為100兆噸）的[[沙皇炸彈|沙皇炸彈]]彈頭。

